data.description: WOW FACTOR! This EXCEPTIONALLY UPGRADED and beautifully designed MUST SEE townhome, is located within the gated community of Regal Palms. Featuring 1,482 square feet, with 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, living room, dining room, and a 2-car parking. Interior upgrades include stainless steel face appliances, the spectacular custom granite in the kitchen and bathrooms, recently repainted, brand new carpets and much more! This home is perfect for entertaining and great for rental income! This home is beautifully furnished, turnkey and ready to go. The gated community of Regal Palms is home to a variety of luxury, resort-inspired amenities including a fitness center, playground, 2 pools, lazy river pool and zero entry, pool side Tiki bar. Sit at your own private beach with the sand volleyball courts. Take advantage of the spa and the indoor play zone, dine in at the restaurant and enjoy the new Banana Jacks!
